Package: wikkitidy
Title: Retrieve Tidy Data from Wikipedia's Many APIs 
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Michael", "Falk", , "michaelgfalk@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9261-8390"))
Description: A wrapper around Wikipedia's major APIs, including the MediaWiki
    Action API and the REST API. Wikipedia's APIs are vast. They provide many
    kinds of data for many purposes. 'wikkitidy' combines these APIs into a
    single interface for researchers, focussing just on those aspects that
    matter most for Wikipedia research.
